Grimmler's a grizzly bear, I think.

::Grimmler::

Grimmler grins at Foxfingers. "Yeah, I'll show you around he says," turning 
to walk toward the Cybertronian Fire.

This bot wasn't bad at all, Grimmler decides, he seemed like he had his head 
on straight.

"But be carefull," he says, "The defences will be watching you, part of a 
security procedure. Any scans or anything will be replied to possibly with 
violence, so be carefull!"

With that, Grimmler walks into the battle cruiser, pausing to let Foxfingers 
catch up.
